= SDL_SetWindowSize =
Use this function to set the size of the window's client area.


== Syntax ==
```c++
void SDL_SetWindowSize(SDL_Window* window,
                       int         w,
                       int         h)
```

== Function Parameters ==
{|
|'''window'''
|the window to change
|-
|'''w'''
|the width of the window ^in pixels^
|-
|'''h'''
|the height of the window ^in pixels^
|}

